    "faq_body": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>.sw-faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;overflow:hidden}.sw-faq-btn{width:100%;background:none;border:none;padding:1.25rem 1rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;gap:1rem}.sw-faq-btn:hover{background:#f9fafb}.sw-faq-q{font-weight:600;color:#111827;font-size:1rem}.sw-faq-icon{width:1.5rem;height:1.5rem;border-radius:50%;background:#EBF2FF;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;transition:transform .2s}.sw-faq-answer{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .3s ease,padding .3s ease}.sw-faq-answer.open{max-height:500px}.sw-faq-answer-inner{padding:.25rem 1rem 1.25rem;color:#6b7280;font-size:.9375rem;line-height:1.7}.sw-faq-cat{font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;color:#083D7D;background:#EBF2FF;padding:.2rem .75rem;border-radius:9999px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:1.5rem}</style><section style=\"padding:4rem 0;background:#f9fafb\"><div style=\"max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem\"><div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem\" id=\"swFaqCats\"><button onclick=\"swFaqFilter('all')\" style=\"padding:.375rem 1rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.875rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid #083D7D;background:#083D7D;color:#fff\">Alle vragen</button><button onclick=\"swFaqFilter('bestelling')\" style=\"padding:.375rem 1rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.875rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid #e5e7eb;background:#fff;color:#374151\">Bestelling</button><button onclick=\"swFaqFilter('levering')\" style=\"padding:.375rem 1rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.875rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid #e5e7eb;background:#fff;color:#374151\">Levering</button><button onclick=\"swFaqFilter('product')\" style=\"padding:.375rem 1rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.875rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid #e5e7eb;background:#fff;color:#374151\">Producten</button><button onclick=\"swFaqFilter('retour')\" style=\"padding:.375rem 1rem;border-radius:9999px;font-size:.875rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid #e5e7eb;background:#fff;color:#374151\">Retour</button></div><div style=\"background:#fff;border-radius:1rem;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);overflow:hidden\"><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"bestelling\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Hoe kan ik een bestelling plaatsen?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Kies je product, voeg het toe aan je winkelwagen en ga naar de kassa. Je kunt betalen met iDEAL, creditcard, Klarna of andere methoden. Je ontvangt na betaling een bevestigingsmail.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"bestelling\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Kan ik mijn bestelling annuleren of wijzigen?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Neem zo snel mogelijk contact op via info@spotwereld.nl of (0)85 060 09 36. Bestellingen die al in verwerking zijn kunnen niet meer worden aangepast.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"bestelling\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Welke betaalmethoden accepteren jullie?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Wij accepteren iDEAL, Visa, Mastercard, Klarna (achteraf betalen), PayPal en Bancontact. Alle betalingen worden beveiligd verwerkt.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"levering\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Hoe lang duurt de bezorging?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Voor 22:00 besteld = volgende werkdag bezorgd. We werken samen met PostNL en DHL voor snelle en betrouwbare bezorging door heel Nederland.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"levering\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Zijn de verzendkosten gratis?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Gratis verzending bij bestellingen van &euro;50 of meer. Onder de &euro;50 rekenen we &euro;4,95 voor standaard bezorging.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"levering\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Kan ik mijn bestelling volgen?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Ja. Zodra je bestelling is verzonden ontvang je een track &amp; trace link per e-mail. Je kunt hiermee de status van je pakket realtime volgen.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"product\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Hoeveel garantie krijg ik op mijn product?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Alle Spotwereld producten hebben standaard 2 jaar garantie. Dit dekt fabricagefouten en materiaaldefecten. Schade door verkeerd gebruik valt niet onder de garantie.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"product\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Zijn de LED spots dimbaar?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Dit verschilt per product. In de productbeschrijving staat duidelijk vermeld of een spot dimbaar is. Let bij dimbare spots op compatibiliteit met je dimmer.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"product\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Wat is het verschil tussen warm wit en koud wit?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Warm wit (2700&ndash;3000K) geeft een gezellig, sfeervol licht &mdash; ideaal voor woonkamers. Koud wit (4000&ndash;6500K) geeft helder, fris licht &mdash; perfect voor keukens en badkamers. Neutraal wit (3500K) zit er tussenin.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"retour\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Hoe retourneer ik een product?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Stuur een e-mail naar info@spotwereld.nl met je ordernummer en reden. Wij sturen je een gratis retourlabel. Lever het pakket in bij een PostNL servicepunt.</div></div></div><div class=\"sw-faq-item\" data-cat=\"retour\"><button class=\"sw-faq-btn\" onclick=\"swFaqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"sw-faq-q\">Wanneer ontvang ik mijn geld terug?</span><span class=\"sw-faq-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#083D7D\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg></span></button><div class=\"sw-faq-answer\"><div class=\"sw-faq-answer-inner\">Na ontvangst en controle van je retour storten we het bedrag binnen 5 werkdagen terug op je rekening of creditcard.</div></div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:3rem;background:#061f40;border-radius:1rem;padding:2rem;text-align:center\"><h3 style=\"color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:1.125rem;margin:0 0 .5rem\">Staat je vraag er niet bij?</h3><p style=\"color:#93c5fd;font-size:.9375rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem\">Ons team helpt je graag persoonlijk verder.</p><a href=\"/pages/contact\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;padding:.75rem 1.75rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#083D7D,#0F6FE3);color:#fff;font-weight:700;border-radius:.625rem;text-decoration:none\">Neem contact op</a></div></div></section><script>function swFaqToggle(btn){var answer=btn.nextElementSibling;var icon=btn.querySelector('.sw-faq-icon');var isOpen=answer.classList.contains('open');document.querySelectorAll('.sw-faq-answer.open').forEach(function(a){a.classList.remove('open');});document.querySelectorAll('.sw-faq-icon').forEach(function(i){i.style.transform='rotate(0deg)';});if(!isOpen){answer.classList.add('open');icon.style.transform='rotate(180deg)';}}function swFaqFilter(cat){document.querySelectorAll('.sw-faq-item').forEach(function(item){item.style.display=(cat==='all'||item.getAttribute('data-cat')===cat)?'block':'none';});document.querySelectorAll('#swFaqCats button').forEach(function(btn){var isActive=btn.getAttribute('onclick').includes(\"'\"+cat+\"'\");btn.style.background=isActive?'#083D7D':'#fff';btn.style.color=isActive?'#fff':'#374151';btn.style.borderColor=isActive?'#083D7D':'#e5e7eb';});}<\/script>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "section_width": "full-width",
        "padding-block-start": 0,
        "padding-block-end": 0
      }
    }
